race.comment: HARTSHORN (1) is in top form including a win by 1.4 lengths over 1000m at Townsville last time out, the second victory on the trot. Sure to measure up again. BLOOMIN' RIPPER (7) racing well with three wins from eight attempts this campaign. Won two starts back at Townsville and was close again last time out. Tyler Leslight who has seven wins when partnering stays on and is sure to play a big role. SATURDAY VIBES (4) returned from a spell a week-and-a-half ago when he was prominent at the bend before being beaten 4.5 lengths into sixth over 1000m at Townsville. Second-up record is sound and is nicely placed to play a pivotal role. The well-related SEVENTIES HIT (8) (half to Hong Kong star Voyage Bubble) scored over 1500m at this track at his most recent appearance on July 24. Worth plenty of thought.
